long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Btcbam light wallet and transaction signing client. support BamSwap.
Btcbam is a light wallet and transaction signing client for decentralized apps (dapps) for the Btcbam blockchain. 

- Send and receive BTCBAM and other BRC20 Tokens.
- Sign transactions sent from decentralized apps

Created by Btcbam development team
